> in the good
> ole rust belt, usually ripped off attached/rusted to the pictured  
> bracket, and
> both discarded long before you bought your bus.  So although the  
> location on
> the fand shroud is actually pretty obvious, the one on the  
> exchanger may be no
> more.  Sometimes just a thin remain of where it was tacked on.
