i think you are confusing this with the alternator bracket/heater box  
connection which is on the right side of a '75-'78 bus. the bracket  
in the OP is for '72-'74 and '79 and it attaches between the shroud  
and the heater box flange. it doesn't attach to a tab of any sort.

